---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CTAButton from '../components/CTAButton.astro';
---

<Layout title="About PizzaWorld - Our Story" description="Learn about PizzaWorld's mission to revolutionize pizza restaurant management with modern technology and innovative solutions.">
  <div class="home-section">
    <div class="content-container">
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h1 class="text-heading text-5xl mb-6">About PizzaWorld</h1>
          <p class="text-subheading text-xl mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            We're on a mission to revolutionize how pizza restaurants operate, one slice at a time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Story Section -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-heading text-3xl mb-6">Our Story</h2>
            <p class="text-body mb-6">
              PizzaWorld was born from a simple observation: pizza restaurants were struggling with outdated systems that couldn't keep up with modern demands. In 2023, our team of restaurant veterans and tech enthusiasts came together to solve this problem.
            </p>
            <p class="text-body mb-6">
              We started with a single pizzeria in downtown, working closely with the owners to understand their pain points. From order management chaos to inventory nightmares, we saw firsthand how technology could transform their operations.
            </p>
            <p class="text-body">
              Today, PizzaWorld serves over 500 restaurants across the country, helping them increase efficiency, reduce costs, and deliver better experiences to their customers.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="modern-card p-8">
            <div class="w-full h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-100 to-orange-200 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-32 h-32 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Mission & Values -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-heading text-4xl mb-12 text-center">Our Mission & Values</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="modern-card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-orange-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-subheading text-xl mb-4">Innovation</h3>
            <p class="text-body">We constantly push the boundaries of what's possible in restaurant technology, always looking for new ways to make operations smoother and more efficient.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="modern-card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-orange-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-subheading text-xl mb-4">Customer Success</h3>
            <p class="text-body">Your success is our success. We're committed to providing exceptional support and ensuring every restaurant using PizzaWorld thrives.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="modern-card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-orange-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-subheading text-xl mb-4">Reliability</h3>
            <p class="text-body">We understand that restaurants can't afford downtime. Our platform is built with reliability and performance as top priorities.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Team Section -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-heading text-4xl mb-12 text-center">Meet Our Team</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="modern-card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
              <span class="text-white text-2xl font-bold">SM</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-subheading text-xl mb-2">Sarah Martinez</h3>
            <p class="text-muted mb-4">CEO & Founder</p>
            <p class="text-body">Former restaurant owner with 15+ years in the industry. Passionate about helping small businesses succeed.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="modern-card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
              <span class="text-white text-2xl font-bold">MJ</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-subheading text-xl mb-2">Mike Johnson</h3>
            <p class="text-muted mb-4">CTO</p>
            <p class="text-body">Tech veteran with experience at major SaaS companies. Leads our engineering team in building robust, scalable solutions.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="modern-card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
              <span class="text-white text-2xl font-bold">LC</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-subheading text-xl mb-2">Lisa Chen</h3>
            <p class="text-muted mb-4">Head of Customer Success</p>
            <p class="text-body">Dedicated to ensuring every PizzaWorld customer gets the most value from our platform.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CTA Section -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <div class="modern-card p-12 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-heading text-4xl mb-6">Join the PizzaWorld Family</h2>
          <p class="text-body text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Ready to see how PizzaWorld can transform your restaurant? Let's start a conversation about your needs.
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
            <CTAButton text="Schedule a Demo" href="/contact" variant="primary" size="lg" />
            <CTAButton text="Contact Us" href="/contact" variant="secondary" size="lg" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout> 